    Note over Cron,Monitor: Reference Folder Monitoring
    Cron->>Monitor: Trigger check
    Monitor->>Process: New PDF detected
    Process->>Embed: Generate embeddings
    Embed->>Process: Return vectors
    Process->>ChromaDB: Store reference vectors
    
    Note over Gradio,LLM: User Document Processing
    Gradio->>Process: Upload document
    Process->>Embed: Generate embeddings
    Embed->>Process: Return vectors
    Process->>ChromaDB: Query compliance
    ChromaDB->>Process: Similarity scores
    Process->>LLM: Check compliance
    LLM->>Gradio: Compliance result